text: Ticocystiscus is a genus of minute sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusc in the family Cystiscidae. This genus, and indeed all the genera in the family, were previously and sometimes still are, placed in the family Marginellidae. == Species == * Ticocystiscus iberia Espinosa & Ortea, 2002 - type species == References == Category:Cystiscidae
title: Ticocystiscus
